{
  "stem": "24614.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had to turn back and come back home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The second time-- and wasn't much later after that-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there were still boats going to England from Ostend, O-S-T-E-N-D-E.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my daddy took us all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we went to Ostend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When we got to Ostend, the last boat had left five minutes before we got there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In Ostend, the Germans were bombing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A lot of bombs were bombing Ostend.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they bombing the-- they were trying to bomb as much of the English soldiers who were there, and the English army, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was hit by a bomb.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I have on my back a little-- for life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- but you don't feel it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "See, the bombs were falling and falling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my sister was near me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I heard the bomb coming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I lie down on top of her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I wanted to protect her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But I was hit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I didn't even know I was hit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "All at once, when it stopped, the bombing stopped, my mother gave a shout, Clara's bleeding!",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they took us into a place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the only thing I remember is that it smelled from a lot of blood.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And it smelled from a lot of iodine and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And there was a priest there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the priest took care of me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And he kept saying to my mother, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "She's not hurt too much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "She'll be all right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he gave me the piece of shrapnel that hurt me-- that had hit me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then we saw that we have to go back home again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we started going back home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Now, when we started going back home, we didn't have any more shoes.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
